  "narrative": "<h3 class=\"story-subheading\">Short impact summary</h3>\n<p class=\"story-text\">The book \"Research-Based Perspectives on the Psychophysiology of Yoga,\" published by IGI Global in 2018, plays a significant role in bridging academic research and practical application in the field of yoga. Although it currently has a limited citation count, its content is ripe for scholarly and policy relevance, as indicated by its moderate uptake within professional and academic circles.</p>\n<h3 class=\"story-subheading\">Full narrative</h3>\n<p class=\"story-text\">The publication \"Research-Based Perspectives on the Psychophysiology of Yoga\" serves as a foundational piece in the growing intersection of psychological and physiological research in the context of yoga practice. Released in 2018, it highlights crucial insights into how yoga impacts mental and physical health, addressing a range of physiological responses associated with this ancient practice. While it has yet to gain prominent visibility through citations or public mentions, its foundational relevance is reinforced by a degree of scholarly uptake, noted with 12 citations in various academic references.</p>\n\n<p class=\"story-text\">The book\u2019s themes contribute to ongoing discussions within both academic and applied settings, where the integration of yoga into therapeutic regimes is becoming increasingly recognized. This relevance extends particularly to sustainability and policy contexts, as evidenced by its connection to one identified Sustainable Development Goal (SDG). Such alignment underscores the potential for yoga to play a vital role in public health and wellness frameworks.</p>\n\n<p class=\"story-text\">Despite the absence of active community discourse on major platforms like Reddit or Wikipedia, the insights presented in this book can inform educators, practitioners, and policymakers alike. The commercial availability of the book on platforms like Amazon and Goodreads suggests a market interest that may translate into further scholarly inquiry and application. </p>\n\n<p class=\"story-text\">Overall, while the current metrics might indicate a need for broader outreach and engagement, the book holds significant potential as a scholarly resource. It lays the groundwork for future research endeavors that could amplify both its academic and societal impact in understanding the psychophysiological dimensions of yoga practice.</p>",
